title: Meridian Brothers - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Meridian Brothers performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded August 3, 2023

Songs:
Puya del empresario
Hipnosis 
Cumbia del pichamán
Metamorfosis

Eblis Alvarez - Vocals, Guitar, Synth
Maria Valencia - Woodwinds, Percussion
Cesar Quevedo Barrero - Bass
Alejandro Forero - Keys
Mauricio Ramirez - Drums

Host: DJ Chilly
Audio Engineers: Kevin Suggs, Julian Martlew
Guest Audio Engineer: Alejandro Araújo Larrahondo
Audio Mixer: Alejandro Araújo Larrahondo
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Ettie Wahl
Editor: Carlos Cruz
